## Project Name

Personal CRM System

---

## Project Description

The Personal CRM System is a web-based application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to efficiently manage personal contacts by adding, editing, searching, and deleting contact information. The application uses Local Storage to save contact details even after the browser is refreshed.

---

## Features

- Add New Contact
- Search Contact
- Edit Contact
- Delete Contact
- Local Storage Support
- User-Friendly Interface

---

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Local Storage

